  "description": "<div>\n  <h4>Application:</h4>\n  <ul>\n    <li>BMW 135i (E82/E88) N54B30 3.0L Turbo, 2008-2010</li>\n    <li>BMW 535i / 535ix (E60/E61) N54B30 3.0L Turbo, 2008-2010</li>\n    <li>BMW Z4 sDrive35i / sDrive35is (E89) N54B30 3.0L Turbo, 2009-2016</li>\n    <li>BMW X6 xDrive35i (F71) N54B30 3.0L Turbo, 2008-2010</li>\n    <li>BMW 740i / 740Li (F01/F02) N54B30 3.0L Turbo, 2010-2012</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"color:#E53333;\"><strong>Will NOT fit 335i</strong></p>\n\n  <h4>Features:</h4>\n  <ul>\n    <li>OE design, handles max power 500HP</li>\n    <li>High quality replacement for factory parts; excellent durability, optimizes vehicle performance</li>\n    <li>Direct replacement for factory part</li>\n    <li>Center rotating bearing housing designed for factory oil and coolant lines</li>\n    <li>Component balanced dynamically more precisely than VSR HIGH SPEED, avg 0.5 mg or less</li>\n    <li>Accessories shown in photos included</li>\n    <li>1-year warranty for manufacturing defects</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h4>Technical Specifications:</h4>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Durable Compressor Wheel: 12(6+6) blades, size: 35.7 x 46 mm</li>\n    <li>Turbine Wheel: 11 blades, size: 35.2 x 40 mm</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"color:#E56600;\">We also sell 17T and 19T N54 Twin Turbos. Contact us if interested.</p>\n\n  <h4>Turbo Part Numbers:</h4>\n  <ul>\n    <li>49131-07000, 49131-07001, 49131-07006, 49131-07007, 49131-07010</li>\n    <li>49131-07011, 49131-07015, 49131-07016, 49131-07107, 49131-07018</li>\n    <li>49131-07019, 49131-07030, 49131-07031, 49131-07040, 49131-07041</li>\n    <li>49131-07065, 49131-07066, 49131-07067, 49131-07068, 49131-07069</li>\n    <li>49131-07075, 49131-07076, 49131-07077, 49131-07078, 49131-07079</li>\n    <li>49131-07161, 49131-07170, 49131-07180, 49131-07205, 49131-07206</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h4>O.E.M Numbers:</h4>\n  <ul>\n    <li>11654564711, 11654564710, 11657563685, 11657563686, 11657583863</li>\n    <li>11657583864, 11657593015, 11657593016, 11657649289, 11657649290</li>\n    <li>4564710, 4564711, 7583863, 7583864, 7593015, 7593016, 7563685, 7563686</li>\n    <li>7649289, 7649290</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n",
